metadata.name: Octo-Witch
metadata.description:
Octo-Witch is the witcher of surreal world and has been designed with the multi-angle art style which is able to turn into another art in the reverse view.
Most of the time Octo-Witch is just a magical beautiful girl but in the situation of danger she can turn into an Octopus,this art perfectly shows us how different personalities can be exist in one soul.
